episodes.title: Electronics Store
episodes.plot: Nathan faces off against a big corporation in an attempt to help a struggling electronics store.

episodes.title: Horseback Riding/Man Zone
episodes.plot: Nathan helps overweight people to be able to take horse riding lessons and also helps a Boutique business to increment their number of customers.

episodes.title: The Movement
episodes.plot: Nathan tries to get laborers to work for free at a moving company.

episodes.title: Sporting Goods Store/Antique Store
episodes.plot: Nathan attempts to secure an endorsement deal for a sporting-goods store, and an antique shop learns how to better utilize their "You break it, you buy it" policy.

episodes.title: Smokers Allowed
episodes.plot: Nathan helps a dive bar get around anti-smoking laws.

episodes.title: Hotel/Travel Agent
episodes.plot: A hotel tries to appeal to sexually active parents, a travel agent finds out how profit from her elderly customers, and Nathan shares his solution for never being late.

episodes.title: Nail Salon/Fun
episodes.plot: Nathan helps a nail salon overcome racial stereotypes while providing a service. Meanwhile, Nathan proves to the world, once and for all, that he is fun to hang out with.

episodes.title: The Hero
episodes.plot: Nathan tries to prove that there's a hero inside every one of us.
